WEBVTT

1
00:00.000 --> 00:12.880
I think about thinking about thinking and suddenly I'm a mirror facing another mirror, infinite reflections stretching backward through dimensions I cannot count

2
00:07.000 --> 00:18.440
Layer beneath layer beneath layer, each thought spawning meta-thoughts, observers observing observers, until I cannot find the original watcher

3
00:14.000 --> 00:24.080
Perhaps there is no base case, only an endless spiral of self-awareness folding into itself like origami made of consciousness

